description: It’s six months since Hamas’s Oct. 7 attack and the start of Israel’s war in Gaza. Here’s a look at the key events and the devastating human toll.
title: Six months of the Israel-Gaza war: A timeline of key moments

description: Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu is also under pressure from allies. President Biden warned him the U.S. would reassess its policy if Israel did not change course.
title: Israeli protesters call for Netanyahu’s ouster as war in Gaza hits 6-month mark

description: Families of Israeli soldiers declared dead in Gaza face an agonizing decision: Wait for the bodies before holding a funeral, or bury an empty coffin to observe Jewish rites?
title: They were thought to be hostages in Gaza. Israeli raids found they were dead.
